title: Liv Tyler enjoys walk in London with baby daughter Luna | Daily Mail Online
text: comments Liv Tyler bundled up on a winter day in London as she took her seven-month-old daughter Luna out for a walk. The 39-year-old actress, who shot to global fame in the The Lord Of The Rings trilogy, wore a voluminous black coat with fur trim around its hood. Beneath the knee-length jacket was a pair of black and grey leggings that tightened about the New York City native's still toned legs. Out and about: Liv Tyler bundled up on a winter day in London as she took her seven-month-old daughter Luna out for a walk She'd popped a pair of cat-eye spectacles on her face, and let her curly hair tumble freely as she walked along, pushing her daughter down the pavement. Lula is her mother's first daughter and her second child by sport agent Dave Gardner, who was best man to David Beckham, per the Evening Standard . Sailor, her first son by Gardner, rang in his second birthday last Sunday. Tyler's also got a 12-year-old son called Milo by Spacehog frontman Royston Langdon, to whom she was married from 2003 until 2008. Safe from the cold: The 39-year-old actress, who shot to global fame in the The Lord Of The Rings trilogy, wore a voluminous black coat with fur trim around its hood The Stealing Beauty star will be among the celebrities plumbing her roots on the American version of Who Do You Think You Are? when it returns to TLC on March 5. In a trailer Entertainment Weekly posted Wednesday, Tyler can be seen leaping around screaming: 'I'm so excited, oh, my God!' She's seen 'Musician' listed as one of her forebears' occupation and notes, at one point: 'So, I really come from music on all sides.' Arm in arm: Lula is her mother's first daughter and her second child by sport agent Dave Gardner, who was best man to David Beckham, per the Evening Standard The two youngest: Sailor, her first son by Gardner, rang in his second birthday last Sunday, and is pictured with his mother sister; Tyler also has a 12-year-old son called Milo by her ex-husband Royston Langdon The daughter of Steven Tyler winds up sitting across her father and telling him one of their ancestors 'was half African American.' Aerosmith's frontman laughs: 'I knew it!' and high-fives his daughter, who is the eldest of his four children and his only progeny by onetime Playmate Bebe Buell. He and his first wife Cyrinda Fox had a now 38-year-old daughter called Mia, and he's had two children - 27-year-old daughter Chelsea and 26-year-old son Taj - by Teresa Barrick, to whom he was married from 1988 until 2006.
